lead_paragraph: A socialite whose weight-loss supplement was linked to suspensions of several NFL players in 2008 for banned substances pleaded guilty on Wednesday to drug misbranding.

headline.main: Socialite Pleads Guilty to Misbranding Drug Tied to NFL Suspensions
